msgctxt "92_Lily"
msgid "Hm..."
msgstr "Mm..."

msgctxt "104_Akiyama"
msgid "Is it somewhere in here?"
msgstr "¿Es por aquí?"

msgctxt "116_Lily"
msgid "Yeah, I think so."
msgstr "Creo que sí..."

msgctxt "128_Lily"
msgid "Though... I don't remember this building being here before."
msgstr "Aunque... No recuerdo que este edificio estuviera aquí."

msgctxt "140_Akiyama"
msgid "Really? It's been around at least as long as I have. Probably way longer."
msgstr "¿Eh? Este edificio ha estado aquí desde hace bastante tiempo."

msgctxt "152_Lily"
msgid "Do you think we could head inside? I'd like to see it for myself if you don't mind."
msgstr "Oye... ¿te molestaría si entramos un momento?"

msgctxt "164_Akiyama"
msgid "Oh, uh, sure..."
msgstr "Oh, ah... claro, no hay problema."

